Package: fracturedetection
Type: Package
Title: Detect and Analyze Fractures in Outcrop Photos
Version: 0.5.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package runs image segmentation on grayscale photographs of 
    outcrops, windows, and hand samples and returns .dxf files of the resulting
    edges along with statistics for structural geology analysis. Makes use of
    the Canny Edge Detector, the Hough Transform, Connected Component Analysis,
    and numerous features from the sp/sf libraries
License: GNU GPL V3
Depends:
    imager,
    raster,
    rgdal,
    rgeos,
    sp,
    sf,
    tidyverse
Suggests:
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
